<seg id="136">  "Every child has known God, not the God of names, not the God of don'ts, but the God who only knows four words and keeps repeating them, saying, 'Come dance with me. Come, dance with me. Come, dance with me.'"  </seg>	<seg id="136"> "Elk kind kent God,  niet de God van bijnamen,  niet de God van doe-niet,  maar de God die slechts vier woorden kent die hij herhaalt,  zeggend: kom dans met mij"  Kom, dans met mij.    </seg>
<seg id="137">  Thank you.  </seg>	<seg id="137"> Dank u.    </seg>
